title: Nathaniel Cole Park Pond
text: Nathaniel Cole Park Pond is a man-made <a href="lake">lake</a> located by <a href="Colesville%2C%20New%20York%23Communities%20and%20locations%20in%20Colesville">West Colesville, New York</a>. Fish species present in the lake include <a href="pumpkinseed%20sunfish">pumpkinseed sunfish</a>, and <a href="smallmouth%20bass">smallmouth bass</a>.
